[%@lib domain_error]
[codeblock:synopsis]
namespace std {
  class domain_error : public logic_error {
  public:
    constexpr explicit domain_error(const string& what_arg);
    constexpr explicit domain_error(const char* what_arg);
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] The class [`domain_error] defines the type of objects thrown as exceptions
by the implementation to report domain errors.
[:zh_CN] [`domain_error] 类定义了作为异常由实现抛出的对象的类型，用以报告值域错误。

[%@lib@ctor domain_error]
[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr domain_error(const string& what_arg);
[codeblock:end]

